'Cosmic Knowledge Transmitter # 8' - (8" x 8" Freehand Drawing on Bristol board) ... Tokens & Talismans have always been used in many different forms by journeymen & shamans to help us to find a free-flowing meditative state, I have created the pieces from this series to help myself to connect with others & to help others connect & share ideas as well as to project a peaceful state of being into the space where they reside. As you stare at the center of these images, your eyes are meant to be guided chaotically through a maze of color - allowing your eyes to wander among the lines will allow the conscious mind to separate from the body and think separately as your physical form continues to exist autonomously - closing your eyes at this moment shall bring you to a place of internal peace where may find yourself transcending time through the power of mind; open your eyes again & you will find a clear head can bring you deep understandings of self. ... This piece & a few others from the series are still looking for a room to bring new light to, DM to acquire for yourself or a friend

🎉🎉RAFFLE RAFFLE 🎉 🎉
Hello VoodooCrew! Welcome to the first raffle being done on this page. On the block today is this beautiful Peter Muller and Jerry Kelly Star Wars themed tube. This piece features 20 stitches, plenty of torn work, and Peters signature button sewed on the front of the tube. Throughout the body you have J Kelly’s Star Wars Millie’s with beautiful fume work in between all the Millie’s. The back also has a huge facet making sure you get lost staring at this tube for hours. Features a removable 2-hole 10mm downstem.
Prize include: Mini Torn Tube W/ downstem. Collab bubble cap between Peter and Jerry. 8/10 used toro grail (30mm) and all this gets shipped in a peli 1150 👊🤘🙏
Rules: $50 for a ticket, no limit on how many tickets you can buy. Once payment is confirmed you can choose whichever number(s) you would like! I will cover shipping as long as it is in the US. If In Canada or another country I ask you cover shipping. Payment via Venmo or PayPal is preferred. If doing PayPal please send Friends and Family to avoid service fees. When it’s filled I’ll go live with a random number generator to decide the winner. Fair for everyone no games or tricks played. No refunds.
